cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper deals with object detection using deep CNNs and active learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The application domain is wildlife conservation, which could also fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of transfer learning and domain adaptation, which could be relevant to computer security (cs.CR).
